ca.mcgill.ecse211.dpmProject

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.dpmProject.Project

  • public class Project
extends java.lang.Object
    this is the main class for Lab 5; it contains almost all the parameters/sensor initiations it will interact with the user through the EV3 module's display and buttons to ask the user whether to initiate testing routine or the demo routine. The routines are performed as consecutive methods within threads
    Author:
    Team12
